{
  "info": {
    "name": "MedChain AI - Complete API",
    "_postman_id": "medchain-ai-2026",
    "description": "MedChain AI - AI-Powered Healthcare Records on Blockchain\n\nComplete REST API with 35+ endpoints.\n\n## Setup\n1. Import this collection\n2. Set `baseUrl` variable to your server (default: http://localhost:5000)\n3. Register a patient & doctor first\n4. Login to get JWT token (auto-saved)\n5. Test all endpoints!\n\n## Auth Flow\n- Register → Login → Token auto-saved → All APIs work\n- For wallet: Connect MetaMask → Sign message → Send signature",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:5000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "doctorToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "patientId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "doctorId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "recordId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "walletAddress", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "description": "Authentication - Register, Login, Wallet Connect",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Patient",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.success) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('patientId', json.data.user._id);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('walletAddress', json.data.user.walletAddress || '');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Zakir Ahmed\",\n  \"email\": \"zakir@medchain.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"role\": \"patient\",\n  \"phone\": \"+923001234567\",\n  \"walletAddress\": \"0xYOUR_PATIENT_WALLET_ADDRESS\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "register"] }
          }
        },
